Map by SubDelt@.
Thx to: Enviolinador, Synopsis, Luffaren, JorisCeoen.
You are NOT allowed under any circumstances to edit or/and reupload the map!
You are NOT allowed under any circumstances to use any parts of the map!

Map based on the Portal game.
Added a new HP-bar system, that shows GLaDOS HP in numbers.
Also added 3 new random paths (4 total).
Rate, comment, play nice and remember: cake is a lie...

-------------------------------------

V3_2 CHANGE LOG:

Lowered GLaDOS' HP;

Attempted to fix HP bar glitches, such as "stucking" image (when screen shows the same time and HP all the time) and "extra HP" (when HP jumps from 0 to 9999). Not sure if it will work on big full servers;

Made the pipe on the upper right path easier to get it;

Fixed items glitch (they wasn't affecting everyone);

Made companion cubes appear on every difficulty, not just EXTREME;

Made companion cube bonuses last every round instead of just one single (bonuses are still random).
